(x-a^2-c^2)(x-b^2-d^2)-(ab+cd)^2=0\\\implies x^2-(a^2+b^2+c^2+d^2)x+(ad-bc)^2=0\\\implies x_\max=\frac{a^2+b^2+c^2+d^2+\sqrt{(a^2+b^2+c^2+d^2)^2-4(ad-bc)^2}}{2}\\=\frac{u+v+2\sqrt{uv}}{4}.
